title: I Have A Question
description: Katie starts with a question about her orchid namesake and her new Doris Burke artwork (10:15). Then, the KAJ gets into the NFL including OBJ's gift for Tom Brady (30:00), Joe Flacco is big mad (47:15) and JJ Watt (56:10). Plus, the Astros hold a 3-2 lead in the World Series but it's the off field problems that has everyone talking (1:24:00), KickballGate (1:41:15) and the NWSL crowns a champion (1:45:00).
